## Edge Functions Local Development

```bash
# Start local Edge Function server
supabase functions serve

# Serve a specific function
supabase functions serve my-function --env-file .env.local

# Call locally
curl -i --location --request POST 'http://localhost:54321/functions/v1/my-function' \
  --header 'Authorization: Bearer [LOCAL_ANON_KEY]' \
  --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  --data '{"name":"World"}'

# Deploy to remote
supabase functions deploy my-function --project-ref [REF]
```

