## Common CLI Errors

| Error | Fix |
|---|---|
| `supabase start` fails | Docker not running — start Docker Desktop first |
| `supabase link` — wrong password | Use DB password from Dashboard → Settings → Database |
| `db diff` shows nothing | Local DB matches migration history — make changes in local Studio first |
| `db push` conflict | Remote has changes not in migration files — run `db pull` first |
| Port 54321 already in use | Another supabase project is running — `supabase stop` first |
| Types out of date | Run `npm run db:types` after every migration push |
